{"id":162117,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/明報-中日軍機戰艦對峙-中國抗議/","date":"2011-06-17T21:30:34Z","modified":"2011-06-17T21:30:34Z","title":"明報 | 中日軍機戰艦對峙 中國抗議","content":"<div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/shim.gif\" alt=\"推\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\"> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p>【明報專訊】中國近日向日方提出強烈抗議，透露日本自衛隊軍艦和軍機4月21日在東海一度與中國海軍艦隊近距離對峙。中方抗議指，在中國艦隊通過靠近沖繩西南諸島的公海時，日方除派導彈驅逐艦跟蹤，還派出武裝直升機對艦隊進行至近距離監視飛行，日方反潛機P3C也在中國艦隊附近低空盤旋，另一架P3C2機並投下數枚偵察潛艇位置的聲納浮標。抗議書指日方做法十分危險。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/shim.gif\" alt=\"推\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20110618%2Fcac1.htm&#038;title=%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E6%88%B0%E8%89%A6%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.